		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000010",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "journeys/Prepping for Storage.md",
			"x": 40,
			"y": 22500,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000011",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Recipe View\n\"Prep for storage\" / \"Start a batch.\" Recipe pre-selected. output_product_id required.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 22100,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 120,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000012",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Recipes List\nQuick action. Recipe must have output_product_id set.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 22300,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000020",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Steps 1–3 — Shared with Cooking a Meal\n\nIdentical flow: select recipe + scale, resolve ingredients (ProductGroup → specific InventoryItem), cook with progressive deduction. Same mid-batch failure handling.\n\n→ *See Journey: Cooking a Meal*\n\n**Guard:** Recipe must have  set. Prompted to link if null.",
			"x": 980,
			"y": 22100,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 280
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Output Product\n\nDetermined by Recipe’s . Shown as header: \"Output: Simple Syrup (64 oz at 2×)\"\n\n**Data:** Recipe (read — output_product_id)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 22680,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 160
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000022",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Single or Split?\n\nChoose how to store output:\n- **Single** — one InventoryItem for full yield\n- **Split** — divide into multiple portions with different quantities/locations",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 22880,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000023",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Single Output Form\n\nQuantity (default=yield), unit, location (required), home location, expiry, notes. One InventoryItem created.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (insert), Flow (insert — purchase), BatchOutput (insert)",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 22680,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000024",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Split Output Form\n\nAdd portion rows: quantity, unit, location (required), expiry, notes. Running total must equal yield. Each portion → one InventoryItem.\n\nCost per unit = total ingredient cost ÷ yield.",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 22920,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000030",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 5 — Complete\n\nSummary: recipe, scale, ingredients used, total cost, output details (portions, locations, cost per unit). Atomic: BatchEvent completed + InventoryItems + BatchOutputs + purchase Flows created.\n\n**Data:** BatchEvent (update), InventoryItem (insert), BatchOutput (insert), Flow (insert — purchase)",
			"x": 2960,
			"y": 22240,
			"width": 420,
			"height": 260
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000050",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/BatchEvent.md",
			"x": 2960,
			"y": 22560,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000051",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/BatchOutput.md",
			"x": 3200,
			"y": 22560,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000052",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/InventoryItem.md",
			"x": 3200,
			"y": 22660,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000060",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Output Definition]**\n\nSingle vs. split toggle. Single: full yield form. Split: portion table with running total, location pickers, cost per portion calculated from ingredients.",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 22440,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "n000000000000061",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Completion Summary]**\n\nRecipe, scale, ingredients summary, output: portions table with quantities + locations + derived costs. Total cost and cost per unit.",
			"x": 2960,
			"y": 22000,
			"width": 420,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000001",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -20,
			"y": 24100,
			"width": 4440,
			"height": 1700,
