		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000011",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Shopping Page\n\"/shopping\" → \"New List\" or select existing active list.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 24300,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000012",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Checking Stock\n\"Add to list\" inline action. Prompts to pick a list, pre-fills Product.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 24480,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000013",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Expiry/Quick-Add\nFrom triage or global quick-add. Prompts for list + Product.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 24660,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000020",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Create New List\n\nName the list (\"H-E-B run\", \"Sysco order\"). Optional notes. Creates ShoppingList (status=active).\n\n**Data:** ShoppingList (insert)",
			"x": 980,
			"y": 24300,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Add Items\n\nSearch with 4 groups:\n- **A:** Inventory (restock targets)\n- **B:** Product catalog\n- **C:** ProductGroups (generic)\n- **D:** Create new\n\nPer-item: quantity, unit, notes. Duplicate detection (merge or separate line). Stay in flow.",
			"x": 1460,
			"y": 24300,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 280
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000022",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### List View\n\nAll items: product, qty, added by, source (Manual/Low stock/Recipe), check status. Actions: add, edit, remove, reorder, mark complete, archive, duplicate, start intake.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (read/update/delete)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 24300,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 240
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000023",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### List Lifecycle\n\n →  (all checked or manual) → \nAuto-complete prompt when last item checked. Reopen possible.\n\nCollaborative: any CrewMember can add/edit/check.",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 24580,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000050",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/ShoppingList.md",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 24300,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000051",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/ShoppingListItem.md",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 24400,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000060",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Shopping List View]**\n\nItem rows with product name, qty, source badge, checkbox. Add items button, list actions toolbar. Collaborative attribution.",
			"x": 1460,
			"y": 24080,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "o000000000000061",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Add Item Search]**\n\n4-group search: inventory restock targets, catalog products, product groups, create new. Per-item fields below.",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 24080,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000001",
			"type": "group",
			"x": -20,
			"y": 26100,
			"width": 4440,
			"height": 1700,
			"color": "4",
			"label": "Journey: Auto-Generated Shopping List"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000002",
			"type": "group",
			"x": 1380,
			"y": 26340,
			"width": 1560,
			"height": 900,
			"color": "6",
			"label": "Auto-Gen: Triggers"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000010",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "journeys/Auto-Generated Shopping List.md",
			"x": 40,
			"y": 26600,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "4"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000011",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Suggested Items List\n\nAuto-created system list per Crew. Receives auto-generated items. Acts as a review queue — items moved to real lists or dismissed.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 26400,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 160,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000020",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Trigger 1 — Low Stock\n\nInventoryItem qty drops below min_stock. Auto-adds to Suggested list (configurable). Qty suggested = deficit to reach min.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (insert — source=low_stock)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 26400,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Trigger 2 — Recipe Needs\n\nIngredients insufficient when planning to cook. \"Shopping needed\" indicator. Suggest and confirm (default) or auto-add.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (insert — source=recipe)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 26640,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000022",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Trigger 3 — Planned Batch\n\nBatch ingredient requirements vs. current inventory. Deficit at planned scale suggested.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (insert — source=meal_plan)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 26880,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000023",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Configuration\n\nPer-Crew in settings:\n- Low stock: auto_add | notify_only | disabled\n- Recipe needs: suggest_confirm | auto_add | disabled\n- Planned batch: suggest_confirm | auto_add | disabled\n\n**Data:** Crew (read settings)",
			"x": 980,
			"y": 26800,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 220
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000024",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Move to Real Lists\n\nFrom Suggested: \"Add to list\" picker → move single, multi-select, or all to a named ShoppingList. Source tracking preserved. Dismiss removes item.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (update/delete)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 26400,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000050",
			"type": "file",
			"file": "entities/ShoppingListItem.md",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 26500,
			"width": 200,
			"height": 60,
			"color": "1"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000060",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Suggested Items]**\n\nItem rows: product, qty suggested, reason (Low stock/Recipe/Batch), current stock. \"Add to list\" and \"Dismiss\" per row. Batch select toolbar.",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 26180,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "p000000000000061",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Trigger Config]**\n\nCrew settings section: 3 trigger toggles (low stock, recipe needs, planned batch) with mode dropdowns.",
