		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000011",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Shopping Page\nSelect active list → \"Start shopping.\" Opens mobile-optimized shopping mode.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 28400,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000020",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Phase 1 — In-Store\n\nMobile-optimized checklist. Tap to check off items (move to \"Found\" section). Actions: uncheck, not available, change qty, add unlisted item. Progress: \"8 of 12 found.\"\n\nCollaborative: multiple CrewMembers can shop same list.",
			"x": 980,
			"y": 28300,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 260
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### In-Store Actions\n\n| Action | Effect |\n|--------|--------|\n| Check off | Item found |\n| Not available | Flagged, excluded from checkout |\n| Change qty | Adjust on the fly |\n| Add unlisted | Quick product search → add |",
			"x": 1460,
			"y": 28300,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 240
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000030",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Checkout Table\n\nChecked items with per-item fields: qty, unit cost (prompted, skippable), restock target resolution. Running trip total.\n\n**Data:** ShoppingListItem (update)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 29020,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000031",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Restock Resolution\n\nPer item: restock existing InventoryItem (pre-selected for low_stock source) or create new. ProductGroup items must resolve to specific Product first.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (read)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 29260,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000032",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Confirm Checkout\n\nSummary: items purchased, unavailable, unlisted, trip total, new vs. restocked. Atomic: purchase Flows + InventoryItem inserts/updates for all items.\n\n**Data:** Flow (insert — purchase), InventoryItem (insert/update)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 29020,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 220
		},
		{
			"id": "q000000000000033",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### After Checkout\n\n\"Ready to put things away?\" → Start intake session (seeded from list) or skip. Unavailable items can be moved to a new list.\n\n→ *See Journey: Intake Session*",
			"x": 2480,
