			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "i000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Section 2 — Quantity\n\nHow much was lost. Smart defaults: countable=1, measured=empty. Cannot exceed current qty. Partial waste indicator shown.\n\n**Data:** none (form state)",
			"x": 1460,
			"y": 32200,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 160
		},
		{
			"id": "i000000000000023",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Reason Details\n\n• **Expired:** expiry date, days past, storage location, opened?\n• **Spoiled:** expiry, storage, container, days open, conditions\n• **Damaged:** how, where, packaging issue?\n• **Prep failure:** recipe, batch, what went wrong, who\n• **Spilled:** where, how, during what\n• **Other:** freeform description",
			"x": 1940,
			"y": 32200,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 300
		},
		{
			"id": "i000000000000061",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "**[MOCK: Reason Picker]**\n\nSix tappable reason cards with icons. Selected card expands into reason-specific detail form below.",
			"x": 1460,
			"y": 31980,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
