			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "m000000000000013",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Kiosk / Dashboard\nRecipe search. Kiosk scoped to crew.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 20260,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "m000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 2 — Review & Resolve\n\nIngredient table with scaled quantities, real-time availability (✅ Ready, 🟡 Short, 🔴 Out, ⚠️ Unresolved). Resolve ProductGroup ingredients to specific InventoryItems (FIFO suggestion). Swap sources, skip ingredients, adjust scale.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (read), ProductGroup (read)",
			"x": 1480,
			"y": 19900,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 280
		},
		{
			"id": "m000000000000022",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 3 — Cook (Deduct As You Go)\n\nRecipe steps displayed alongside ingredients. \"Use\" button per ingredient creates prep_usage Flow + BatchInput immediately. Cached quantity decremented. Short items deduct what’s available.\n\n**Data:** Flow (insert — prep_usage), BatchInput (insert), InventoryItem (update qty)",
			"x": 1480,
			"y": 20240,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 280
		},
		{
			"id": "m000000000000023",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Mid-Batch Failure\n\n\"Something went wrong.\" Options:\n- **Log as waste** → Logging Waste (reason=prep_failure, batch linked)\n- **Keep deductions** → batch cancelled, used ingredients stay deducted\n- **Undo** → compensating Flows restore quantities",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 20700,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200,
			"color": "3"
		},
		{
			"id": "m000000000000030",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 4 — Complete\n\nAll ingredients used/skipped. Summary: recipe, scale, ingredients used/short/skipped, total cost, cost per yield unit. BatchEvent completed.\n\n**Data:** BatchEvent (update — status=completed, total_cost)",
			"x": 2000,
			"y": 20040,
			"width": 400,
			"height": 220
		},
