			"width": 400,
			"height": 180,
			"color": "2"
		},
		{
			"id": "h000000000000030",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Tab 1 — Triage\n\nAll items in Expired/Urgent/Warning tiers sorted by urgency. Actions: Use it (consumption Flow), Waste it (→ Logging Waste), Extend date, Dismiss. Batch triage via checkboxes.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (read/update), Flow (insert)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 30200,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 220
		},
		{
			"id": "h000000000000031",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Triage Actions\n\n| Action | Effect |\n|--------|--------|\n| Use it | Consumption Flow, qty deducted |\n| Waste it | → Logging Waste (reason=expired) |\n| Extend date | Update expiry_date |\n| Dismiss | UI-only, reappears next time |",
			"x": 1940,
			"y": 30200,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 280
		},
		{
			"id": "h000000000000032",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Tab 2 — FIFO Planning\n\nItems grouped by Product, sorted nearest-expiry first. FIFO alerts: \"✅ Use this first\" or \"⚠️ Use immediately\". Actions: Use it, Move to front (→ Moving Items).\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (read), Product (read)",
			"x": 1440,
