		},
		{
			"id": "h000000000000033",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Tab 3 — Missing Dates\n\nItems where expiry_date is null. Batch-set via date picker per row or \"Select all + set date.\" \"No expiry needed\" toggle per item. Metadata only — no Flows.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (update expiry_date)",
