			"text": "### Entry: Scheduled Job\nConfigurable cadence (daily/weekly/monthly). Background system reconciliation.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 36380,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000013",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Entry: Dashboard Alert\n\"Reconciliation found 3 discrepancies.\" Links to review screen.",
			"x": 520,
			"y": 36560,
			"width": 340,
			"height": 100,
			"color": "5"
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000020",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### System Reconciliation\n\nFor every InventoryItem: compare cached  vs. sum of all Flows. Flag discrepancies. Scheduled (cron) or manual trigger.\n\n**Data:** InventoryItem (read), Flow (read — aggregate sum)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 36140,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 220
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000021",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Review Discrepancies\n\nItems where cached ≠ Flow sum. Per item: Correct (adjustment Flow), Investigate (show Flow history), Dismiss. \"Correct all\" bulk action.\n\n**Data:** Flow (insert — adjustment), InventoryItem (update qty)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 36400,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000022",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Reconciliation Config\n\nPer-Crew in settings:\n: daily | weekly | monthly | disabled\nDiscrepancies flagged for admin — never auto-corrected.",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 36140,
			"width": 360,
			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000030",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 1 — Define Scope\n\nChoose what to count: full inventory, by Space (with children toggle), or by Category.\n\n**Data:** Space (read), Category (read)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 36940,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000031",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 2 — Count\n\nCount sheet: items with location, expected qty hidden (prevents bias). Enter actual counts. \"Not found\" (qty=0), \"Found extra.\" Auto-saves. Progress indicator.\n\n**Data:** client-side (auto-save)",
			"x": 1440,
			"y": 37160,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 220
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000032",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 3 — Review Discrepancies\n\nExpected vs. counted. Per item: Adjust (adjustment Flow + reason), Recount, Dismiss. Only discrepancies shown by default.\n\n**Data:** Flow (insert — adjustment), InventoryItem (update qty)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 36940,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000033",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Step 4 — Complete Audit\n\nSummary: scope, items counted, matches, adjusted, dismissed, net adjustment value. All adjustments share audit_session_id.\n\n**Data:** Flow (insert — batched adjustments)",
			"x": 1960,
			"y": 37180,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 200
		},
		{
			"id": "r000000000000034",
			"type": "text",
			"text": "### Audit History\n\nPrevious results: date, type, scope, discrepancy rate, net adjustment. Tap for full detail from that audit.\n\n**Data:** Flow (read — by audit_session_id)",
			"x": 2460,
			"y": 36940,
			"width": 380,
			"height": 180
		},
